---
title: Org / Project Selection flow
---
flowchart TD
    ORG{One org or many?}
    ORG -->|one| ORG_CONFIRM{"Use this org?"}
    ORG -->|many| ORG_PICKER["Picker: existing orgs + 'Create new'"]
    ORG_CONFIRM -->|yes| PROJECT
    ORG_CONFIRM -->|no, create new| ORG_NAME["Text input: name your org"] --> PROJECT
    ORG_PICKER -->|existing org selected| PROJECT
    ORG_PICKER -->|create new| ORG_NAME

    PROJECT{One project or many?}
    PROJECT -->|one| PROJ_CONFIRM{"Use this project?"}
    PROJECT -->|many| PROJ_PICKER["Picker: existing projects + 'Create new'"]
    PROJ_CONFIRM -->|yes| DONE
    PROJ_CONFIRM -->|no, create new| PROJ_NAME["Text input: name your project"] --> DONE
    PROJ_PICKER -->|existing project selected| DONE
    PROJ_PICKER -->|create new| PROJ_NAME
    DONE["→ continue"]